<para>Undo your delete by pressing <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> or by clicking the arrow in the <guilabel>Playlist Toolbar</guilabel> at the bottom of the <guilabel>Playlist</guilabel> pane (see below).
</para>
</sect3>
