</para>
<para>By default, your saved playlist has a name composed of the date and time when you saved it (see image below). Right-click the playlist name to rename it. Right-clicking on a playlist name also allows you to add it to your existing playlist in the <guilabel>Playlist</guilabel> pane, or to replace your existing playlist.
</para>
