<para>To share the folder, just check the <guilabel>Share with Samba (Microsoft Windows)</guilabel> field and set the share name under the <guilabel>Name</guilabel> field. Check the <guilabel>Allow Guests</guilabel> checkbox to allow anonymous users access to the folder.
