<sect3 id="troubleshooting-media-device-support"><title>Troubleshooting Media Device support</title> 
<para>As of Amarok 2.8, the following devices should work with Amarok:
</para>
<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Generic Media Players connected through the UMS protocol.</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>iPods/iPhones, depending on their support by the libgpod library. The status depends on the version of this library installed on your system, please refer to <ulink url="http://www.gtkpod.org/wiki/Home">the libgpod support listing</ulink> on their homepage.</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>limited support for devices using the MTP protocol, the support for new Android devices is currently implemented for the next Amarok version.</para></listitem>
</itemizedlist>
</sect3>
