<sect3 id="edit-several-tracks"><title>Edit Several Tracks</title> 
<para>Several tracks can be selected by clicking on the artist, album, or genre in the your collection or by selecting several tracks in the playlist using the &Ctrl; (non-sequential) or &Shift; (sequential) key.
