<sect1 id="queue-manager"><title>Queue Manager</title> 
<para>Tracks are loaded in the <guilabel>Playlist</guilabel>. In normal track progression, when a song is over, the next one played is the one below the just-played one. The <emphasis>Queue</emphasis> is one way to change the order in which the songs are played.
