<sect3 id="bookmark-manager"><title>Bookmark Manager</title> 
<para>The bookmark manager allows you to bookmark different kinds of things to recall them later. You can also create folders to organize your collection of bookmarks. The search box provides a convenient way to find bookmarks. The context menu offers the possibility to <guilabel>Load</guilabel> and <guilabel>Delete</guilabel> the bookmark.
</para>
<para>
<screenshot>
