</para>
</sect3>
<sect3 id="equalizer"><title>Equalizer</title> 
<para>Provides the possibility to configure sound settings. You can choose between manually adjusting the settings and using templates. Right now, the <emphasis>Phonon</emphasis> <emphasis>GStreamer</emphasis> is required for a functional equalizer.
</para>
<para>
<screenshot>
<screeninfo></screeninfo>
