    </textobject>
  </mediaobject>
</screenshot>
</para>
</sect3>
<sect3 id="network-requests-viewer"><title>Network Requests Viewer</title> 
<para>The <guilabel>Network Requests Viewer</guilabel> allows you to monitor the network requests made by &amarok;. Selecting this option will open this window:
</para>
<para>
<screenshot>
<screeninfo></screeninfo>
