</para>
</sect3>
<sect3 id="update-collection"><title>Update Collection</title> 
<para>Checks the files in the folders you defined as your collection. New files will be added and missing ones removed from the left pane.
</para>
</sect3>
<sect3 id="synchronize-statistics"><title>Synchronize Statistics</title> 
<para>This option allows you to synchronize statistics of your various collections. This is a new feature in &amarok; since version 2.7 For more information, see also <link linkend="statistics-synchronization">Statistics Synchronization Between Collections and with Last.fm</link> in the handbook.
</para>
</sect3>
</sect2>
