</para>
</sect3>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="amarok-shortcuts"><title>Amarok Shortcuts</title> 
<para>Control &amarok; using <emphasis>keyboard shortcuts</emphasis>, which are combinations of keys which each control a specific action. &amarok; has default shortcuts, but you can also make your own.
