    <entry>
    <para>Print the list of shortcuts.</para>
    </entry>
  </row>
  <row>
    <entry>
    <para><guilabel>OK</guilabel></para>
    </entry>
    <entry>
    <para>Save all changes.</para>
    </entry>
  </row>
  <row>
    <entry>
    <para><guilabel>Cancel</guilabel></para>
    </entry>
    <entry>
    <para>Close window without saving changes.</para></entry>
  </row>
  </tbody>
  </tgroup>
</informaltable>
</para>
<para>When you select an action, that opens a sub-window where you can choose between two radio buttons, <guilabel>Default</guilabel> and <guilabel>Custom</guilabel>. If you choose <guilabel>Default</guilabel> you'll use the default shortcut. If you choose <guilabel>Custom</guilabel> you'll configure and use your shortcut for this action.
</para>
